---
---
<section id="problem" class="min-h-screen flex items-center py-16 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Problem</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">
        Building Customer Intelligence is <span class="gradient-text">Hard</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#A1A1AA] text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        You want to learn from every interaction. But tool sprawl and manual workflows make it hard to turn that data into real insight.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-10">

      <!-- 1. Most interactions go unanalyzed -->
      <div class="border-l-2 border-red-500/30 pl-6">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-red-500/8 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F87171" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
            <path d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#E4E4E7] mb-1">Most interactions go unanalyzed</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed mb-3">Sales calls, emails, and support tickets pile up every day. No one has time to review them all.</p>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-2 bg-[#0a0a0d] border border-white/[0.04]">
          <div class="flex gap-1.5 flex-wrap">
            {["call_mar3.mp4", "inbox_247.csv", "ticket_1892", "notes.docx"].map(f => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/10">
                <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none"><rect x="1" y="1" width="6" height="6" rx="1" stroke="rgba(248,113,113,0.4)" stroke-width="0.75"/></svg>
                <span class="text-[11px] text-red-400/70 font-mono">{f}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-[#52525B] mt-1 text-center">Unreviewed · piling up</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Data lives in silos -->
      <div class="border-l-2 border-orange-500/30 pl-6">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-orange-500/8 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FB923C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
            <rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
            <rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
            <rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#E4E4E7] mb-1">Data lives in silos</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed mb-3">Interactions live across CRM, support tools, product systems, and call platforms. No team has the full picture.</p>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-2 bg-[#0a0a0d] border border-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-between gap-1.5 flex-wrap">
          {["CRM", "Support", "Product", "Calls"].map(s => (
            <span class="text-[11px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-orange-500/5 border border-orange-500/10 text-orange-400/80 font-medium">{s}</span>
          ))}
          <span class="text-[11px] text-[#52525B] flex items-center gap-0.5">
            <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            No connection
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Status depends on who you ask -->
      <div class="border-l-2 border-yellow-500/30 pl-6">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-yellow-500/8 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FACC15" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/>
            <path d="M12 17h.01"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#E4E4E7] mb-1">Status depends on who you ask</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed mb-3">One rep says the deal will close. Another says it's slipping. Leaders struggle to know what's real.</p>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-2 bg-[#0a0a0d] border border-white/[0.04] flex gap-2">
          <div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-1 rounded bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20">
            <span class="text-[11px] text-green-400 font-medium">Rep A:</span>
            <span class="text-[11px] text-green-400/90">Will close ✓</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-1 rounded bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20">
            <span class="text-[11px] text-red-400 font-medium">Rep B:</span>
            <span class="text-[11px] text-red-400/90">Slipping</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Data trapped in vendor tools -->
      <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-500/30 pl-6">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-amber-500/8 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#E4E4E7] mb-1">Data trapped in vendor tools</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed mb-3">Conversation platforms lock interaction data inside their apps. Getting it into your data warehouse is painful.</p>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-2 bg-[#0a0a0d] border border-white/[0.04] flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20">
            <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[11px] text-amber-400/90 font-medium">Vendor app</span>
          </div>
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#71717A" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-red-500/20 bg-red-500/5">
            <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F87171" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[11px] text-red-400/80">Data warehouse</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
